<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">1月21日上午，全省教育系统召开紧急会议，对做好寒潮天气防范暨寒假春节期间学校安全稳定工作进行全面部署。省委教育工委书记、省教育厅厅长吴永明出席并讲话。会议以视频形式召开，全省教育系统6000余人在分会场参加会议。<span style="list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">会议强调了做好寒潮天气防范暨寒假春节期间学校安全稳定工作的重要性，并对全省教育系统提出要盯紧盯牢重点工作，要切实加强应急准备，要强化责任落实三点要求。</span>&nbsp;我校在行政楼一楼会议室设会场，参与这次会议。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2020%3A05%3A13DSC09532.JPG?Expires=2021285114&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=v8jDxMnZd1LW7omKDSM3mFk8zlU%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">当天下午，学校迅速反应，严密部署，并及时召开寒潮天气防范暨寒假春节期间安全稳定工作部署会。党委书记、督导专员江延湖，党委副书记、副校长高建国出席会议。相关职能部门主要负责同志参加会议。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2020%3A06%3A34DSC09742.JPG?Expires=2021285195&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=XwnPAnTpsDzEyzifH5GAczbfqJA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">会议要求：一是各部门、学院主要负责同志要认真学习领会、落实落地上级关于高校安全稳定和应对寒潮天气的工作部署，增强敏感性、忧患意识，克服麻痹大意思想、情绪，切实扛起责任，主动谋划，积极作为，守好地、看好们、管好人。二是对师生组织一次安全教育，提高全校师生的安全意识。三是认真组织安全排查，及时整改，把隐患及时排除。四是加强在校人员安全管理，按照谁使用、谁管理、谁负责的原则，严格查寝、销假制度，重视人文关怀，做好服务保障。五是重视做好应急处置工作，完善应急预案，做好人员分工、物资准备和巡检巡查、舆情引导管控等相关工作。六是加强校园假期治安、施工、交通等安全管理工作，坚决筑牢校园安全稳定坚固防线，以“大抓落实年”的实绩实效，全力守护师生生命安全和身心健康，为全省“两会”顺利召开、师生欢度寒假春节创造安全稳定的社会环境。</span></p><div class="foot_background_color" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: rgb(135, 40, 170); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap;"></div><p><br/></p>